# MCP Server Configuration Template for ANOINT Array
# 
# ⚠️  SECURITY WARNING ⚠️
# This is a TEMPLATE file - DO NOT add real credentials here!
# 
# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.mcp.local
# 2. Fill in your actual values in .env.mcp.local (never commit this file)
